x4freetext: Inelastic scattering of 14 MeV neutrons by
The D(d,n)3He reaction also was used as neutron
source to obtain the detector efficiency for low energy
.Cylindrical, 2.54 cm diam, 2.54 cm long, at 7.3 cm
from the neutron source, natural elements, isotopic
compositions given in table 1 of NST,11,(12),523,1974
scattered neutron spectra. 80 cm flight path.
diam, 5.08 cm long, connected with two 56 AVP
A.P.T. Japan code changed to jpn
